info.author: Cerato Daniele
info.description: This program tries to convert an HEC-RAS GIS export file to a graphical file. You can choose between a .dxf file, suitable for CAD applications, and a .sql file, useful for GIS applications.
info.name: RAS2map.py
info.summary: Convert an HEC-RAS GIS export file to a .dxf or .sql file.
info.html_description: This program tries to convert an HEC-RAS GIS export file to a graphical file. You can choose between a .dxf file, suitable for CAD applications, and a .sql file, useful for GIS applications.
